metadata.name: Nirvana
metadata.description:
I can be beautiful, and I can be the ugly one.
I can gift the wisdom, and I can fulfill the stupidest things.
I can bring the most idiotic to the best positions, making the wisest do the most foolish things.
I can summon the devil to heaven and drive the Human away from the same paradise.
You will find me in the farthest stones and the nearest veins.
The name is Love, The first endless angel.
